msgstr ""

#: ../../../../docstring of numpy.random._generator.Generator:38
msgid "Recommended constructor for `Generator`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../docstring of numpy.random._generator.Generator:43
msgid ""
"The Python stdlib module :external+python:mod:`random` contains pseudo-"
"random number generator with a number of methods that are similar to the "
"ones available in `Generator`. It uses Mersenne Twister, and this bit "
"generator can be accessed using `MT19937`. `Generator`, besides being NumPy-"
"aware, has the advantage that it provides a much larger number of "
"probability distributions to choose from."
msgstr ""

